snippet.title: Sonic Twitter Takeover #4 - All Answers
snippet.description:
Sonic, Tails, Shadow and Dr. Eggman joined us for our fourth ever Twitter Takeover! Here's a collection of all the answers, which were written and recorded over a single day! Special thanks to our amazing cast: Roger Craig Smith (Sonic), Mike Pollock (Eggman), Kirk Thornton (Shadow), and Colleen O’Shaughnessey (Tails) for hanging out with us and answering so many questions! 

And a special thanks to ALL OF YOU for sending so many questions and for trending us #1 Worldwide and in the USA! 

Sonic Twitter Takover #4 - Credits:

Voice of Sonic - Roger Craig Smith
Voice of Eggman - Mike Pollock
Voice of Shadow - Kirk Thornton
Voice of Tails - Colleen O'Shaughnessy 

Writing: Aaron Webber
Video Editing: BLKBX Creative Group
Post Management: Katie Chrzanowski 

Follow us on Twitter in case we do another someday: https://twitter.com/sonic_hedgehog

And you can buy Team Sonic Racing (out now!) at: https://www.sonicthehedgehog.com/teamsonicracing
